{
  "stem": "1132.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, you have to understand the interplay of war going on, bombs being dropped, fighting going on on the streets.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You having to wear the yellow Star of David as a little kid.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At the end, not being able to get out on the streets, because it was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and you just absolutely were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was A, dangerous, B, you were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And being in a situation with 15 other people in a room, and you being hungry more often than not.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's a pretty amazing confluence of events and circumstances that make for somebody's understanding or trying to understand, and the memories that that leaves, and how one develops as a result of these factors.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It also creates for a very tight family, a nuclear family that is very tight and in many ways very unique as I later on learned in life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were looking at me that you were the only one who has both parents there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you were a Jewish kid and you had both of your parents, that was unheard of during the time when I was growing up after the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think all I wanted is the shooting to stop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And all I wanted is to quote, 'be able to go home.' I think that's all I wanted.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- that's-- and of course, I was supposed to start first grade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was supposed to be in first grade in September of '44, which never happened.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have a very clear recollection of that also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't go-- you don't not go to school because you are a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You don't go to school because nobody else is going to school because there is a war going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
